org.openstreetmap.josm.plugins.mapillary.downloads

Class MapillaryExportManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openstreetmap.josm.gui.PleaseWaitRunnable
      • org.openstreetmap.josm.plugins.mapillary.downloads.MapillaryExportManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, ProgressMonitor.CancelListener

    public class MapillaryExportManager
extends PleaseWaitRunnable
    Export main thread. Exportation works by creating a MapillaryExportWriterThread and several MapillaryExportDownloadThread. The second ones download every single image that is going to be exported and stores them in an ArrayBlockingQueue. Then it is picked by the first one and written on the selected folder. Each image will be named by its key.
    Author:
    nokutu
